#EditNotifModal.modal.fade(role='dialog')
    .modal-dialog.modal-lg(role='content')
        .modal-content
            .modal-header
                h4.modal-title Edit Notification
                button.close(type='close', data-dismiss='modal') &times;
            .modal-body
                form 
                    if user 
                        .form-group.row
                            label.col-md-12.col-form-label(for='editTittle') Tittle
                                span 
                                    i(class="fas fa-pen")
                            .col-md-12
                                input(required, disabled,  class="form-control", type="text", name="editTittle", id="editTittle", value="HỌC TẬP TRUNG TẠI TRƯỜNG TỪ NGÀY 08/03/2020")
                        .form-group.row
                            label.col-md-12.col-form-label(for='editContent') Content
                                span 
                                    i(class="fas fa-pen")
                            .col-md-12
                                textarea(disabled, class="form-control text-justify", id="editContent", rows="4" , required) HSSV sẽ trở lại học tập trung tại Trường từ ngày 8/3/2021 theo thời khóa biểu của Nhà trường. Trước khi trở lại Trường học tập trung, HSSV thực hiện khai báo lịch trình di chuyển trên hệ thống thông tin sinh viên từ ngày 26/02/2021. HSSV chủ động thực hiện các biện pháp phòng, chống dịch bệnh COVID-19 theo khuyến cáo của Bộ Y tế và các cơ quan chức năng; Thực hiện nghiêm túc “Thông điệp 5K”: Khẩu trang – Khử khuẩn – Khoảng cách – Không tập trung – Khai báo y tế.
                        .form-group.row
                            label.col-md-12.col-form-label(for='editType') Type
                                span 
                                    i(class="fas fa-pen")
                            .col-md-12
                                input(required, disabled,  class="form-control", type="text", name="editType", id="editType", value="Phòng Đại Học")
                        .form-group.row
                            label.col-md-12.col-form-label(for='editAttachment') Attachment
                                span 
                                    i(class="fas fa-pen")
                            .col-md-12
                                input(disabled, accept="image/*", type="file", name="imageNotification", id="editAttachment", class="form-control")
                        .form-group.row
                            .col-md-12.justify-content-center.d-flex
                                    p(class="mb-0 text-success", id="updateNotifSuccess")
                                    p(class="mb-0 text-danger", id="updateNotifError")
                            .col-md-12.justify-content-end.d-flex
                                button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit', id='btnUpdateNotif', disabled='disabled') Update
                                button.btn.btn-default.ml-3(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Close
